  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>With a good balance of weaponry, shielding and speed,
  Cruisers are the primary strike ships of an empire.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>They are excellent ships for offensive operations again=
st other
  empires. They form the back-bone of your attack fleets.<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Cruisers are heavily armed and defended. They carry tro=
ops
  for ground invasion along with multiple torpedo weapons for heavy orbital
  bombardment. Cruisers sometimes also carry area weapons</span>.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>To supply the high power requirements of their heavy
  weaponry, Cruisers usually have multiple reactors.</span><span lang=3DEN-=
GB
  style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><o:p></o:p></span></p>
